  line `[ See s ection s 32( 2 ) and 38]`
  line `1. The Uttar Pradesh Advocates’ Welfare Fund Act, 1974 (6 of 1974).`
  line `2. The Bihar State Advocates’ Welfare Fund Act, 1983 (16 of 1983).`
  line `3. The Madhya Pradesh Adhivakata Kalyan Nidhi Adhiniyam, 1982 (9 of 1982).`
