  line `12. The Himachal Pradesh Advocates ’ Welfare Fund Act, 1996 (14 of 1996).`
  line `13. The Kerala Advocates’ Welfare Fund Act, 1980 (21 of 1980).`
  line `14. The Karnataka Advocates’ Welfare Fund Act, 1983 (2 of 1985).`
  line `15. The West Ben gal Advocates ’ Welfare Fund Act, 1991 (XIII of 1991).`
  line `16. The Jammu and Kashmir Advocates ’ Welfare Fund Act, 1997 (XXVI of 1997).`
  line __________
